hey dave  Anything is possible. There are two types of carriers, the  early 
ones had a bucket that the gear rode in, the later had a slot that matched  up 
to the gear. I could see this type doing it more so than the older one. I  
have never seen it happen in my 40 years of working on them , but that  doesn't 
mean it couldn't. No offense meant.  later  mark  d



